    {
      "height": 411,
      "id": "2ff6e78cd0370e27",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Explore the fact that [[Chandroid]] can remember commands. Look through door, place command marker.",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": -3810,
      "y": 1870
    },
    {
      "height": 389,
      "id": "15b6bc5acadcd866",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "puzzle with pressing q on lift and releasing it down\n\n(must fix bug where she doesn't move)",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": -3490,
      "y": 1870
    },
    {
      "height": 230,
      "id": "11800e9a67e518f4",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "in cutscene when chandroid finds her battery is useless, she's kneeling facing away from the player/camera to enphasize the emotion",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 410,
      "x": -4720,
      "y": 2165
    },
    {
      "height": 717,
      "id": "0b252a5ebc999330",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "#### Models to make\n ~~tree~~\n ~~bench~~\n  ~~metal gate?~~\n ~~awning~~\n ~~door?~~\n ~~planter pot~~\n statuette\n ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 320,
      "x": -4630,
      "y": 857
    },
    {
      "height": 717,
      "id": "f04c2bf168500320",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "##### Things to decorate\n* buildings\n\t* windows\n\t* doors\n\t* sides\n* benches\n* tree leaves\n* metal bars/fence\n* iron gate\n* statuettes\n* restaurant area\n\t* tables\n\t* chairs\n\t* floor\n\t* countertop\n\t* props\n* centerpiece ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 330,
      "x": -3850,
      "y": 857
    },
    {
      "height": 717,
      "id": "8c7679cdb69bec3b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "* decorate rooms\n* create apartment\n* create dragon boss\n* create characters\n* add cutscenes\n* add feedback to lever/button models",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 355,
      "x": -3450,
      "y": 857
    },
    {
      "height": 212,
      "id": "d9118a2b698e92e2",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "- Sprocket gun golf\n- Sprocket gun bowling\n- Sprocket gun baseball\n- Sprocket gun shot put/distance challenge",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 525,
      "x": -4425,
      "y": 1874
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 717,
      "id": "57935775d1cd0527",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Textures to make\n\n* ~~metal fence top~~\n* metal gate?\n* ~~window pane~~\n* ~~window shutters~~\n* tabletop\n* leaves\n* awning/cloth\n* futuristic wall panel (animated)\n* front door?\n* ~~skyscraper window~~\n* 2 brick variations\n* 3 floor tile variations",
