    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 334,
      "id": "a145ef5a45478886",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "border": "dashed"
      },
      "text": "Forget this ",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 574,
      "x": -1824,
      "y": -4200
    },
    {
      "color": "3",
      "height": 260,
      "id": "ad2fc6c995a8142b",
      "styleAttributes": {
        "border": "dashed"
      },
      "text": "Approach the game in different orders depending\non what upgrades you've found\n\nBeat bosses in multiple orders\n\nExcept then you'd need to make each path potentially linear and not cross-compatible",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 620,
      "x": -4013,
      "y": -4353
    },
    {
      "color": "2",
      "height": 60,
      "id": "8cdf39edcaf78ef6",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "[[Tablet]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 250,
      "x": -2814,
      "y": -4760
    },
    {
      "height": 640,
      "id": "61e7501606c8aaec",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Upgrades:\n- [[Rewire]]\n- [[Sprocket Gun]]\n- [[Tablet]]\n- [[Chainsaw]]\n- [[Breathing Device]]\n- [[Floaties]]\n- [[Shoulder Upgrade]]\n- [[Bouncy Skirt]]\n- [[Metal Boots]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 640,
      "x": -8800,
      "y": -3500
    },
    {
      "height": 280,
      "id": "9ae6006066333c8c",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Maguffins:\n- [[Chainsaw]]\n- [[Codecs]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 640,
      "x": -8800,
      "y": -2800
    },
    {
      "height": 640,
      "id": "603c00a0f73ee05a",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Puzzle mechanics:\n- Pad\n- Door\n- Dog\n- Sprocket Push\n- Sprocket 2D Push\n- Lift\n- Rewire\n- Weighted Pad + Weight\n- Thug\n- Snatcher\n- Power Source\n- Repeater\n- Carryable Pad\n- Moving Sidewalk",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 780,
      "x": -8060,
      "y": -3500
    },
    {
      "color": "8",
      "height": 90,
      "id": "9247b6f8e94c5a7e",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "Lots of good outfits here",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 260,
      "x": -2094,
      "y": -3270
    },
    {
      "color": "7",
      "height": 60,
      "id": "184a0a3a2a9c1e8e",
