      "y": -3540
    },
    {
      "height": 1300,
      "id": "1c11ab79195b7f5b",
      "styleAttributes": {
      },
      "text": "### Ch. 1\nOpening---[[DnD Nerd]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Inspector Specs]]\n[[Quantum Traveling Device]]\n[[Metal Boots]]\n[[Rewire]]\n[[Bouncy Skirt]]\n\n### Ch. 2--A\nHighway---Blocked Suburb Entrance (rocks)\n\nRequires:\n[[Shoulder Upgrade]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Floaties]]\n\n### Ch. 2--B\nSewer---[[Tech Nerd]]\n\nRequires:\n[[Floaties]]\n\nAbilities:\n[[Shoulder Upgrade]]\n\n### Ch. 3\nSuburbs---[[Fangirl Nerd]]",
      "type": "text",
      "width": 1350,
      "x": -80,
      "y": -3540
